title: Troubleshoot UD/UCMDB
content:
This section provides troubleshooting documentation links for classic and containerized UD/UCMDB.

Classic UD/UCMDB

See the Troubleshooting instructions for classic UD/UCMDB. 

Containerized UD/UCMDB

See the Troubleshooting instructions for containerized UD/UCMDB. 

Note: To troubleshoot installation issues for containerized UD/UCMDB, see Troubleshoot installation.

To find the log files for containerized UD/UCMDB, see Find UD/UCMDB log files.
